<storybody><![CDATA[<p>While the country continues to remain torn over Tanmay Bhat's little Snapchat stint, actor-comedian Gaurav Gera has gone ahead and posted a video about the same. </p><p>In his latest video, the actor who is known for his Shopkeeper-Behenji Instagram series, face-swapped with Lata Mangeshkar--much like Tanmay Bhat did--and made an extremely valid point about the controversy. </p><p><i>"Video agar funny hota, toh main khud shayad use share bhi karti, use share na karna mere khayal se kaafi hai, usse zyada main Tanmay ka bura nahi chahti," </i>(Had the video been funny, I would've shared it myself, so the very act of not sharing is enough; I have no ill feelings towards Tanmay otherwise), Gaurav says.</p><p><b>Also Read: <a href="http://indiatoday.intoday.in/story/sachin-lata-video-roast-15-tongue-in-cheek-tweets-on-the-tanmay-bhat-video/1/681492.html" target="_blank" mce_href="http://indiatoday.intoday.in/story/sachin-lata-video-roast-15-tongue-in-cheek-tweets-on-the-tanmay-bhat-video/1/681492.html"><u>Sachin-Lata video roast: 15 tongue-in-cheek tweets on the Tanmay Bhat video</u></a> </b></p><p>Echoing a view that has been doing the rounds since the time of the controversy's inception, Gaurav also speaks on the lines of how we as a nation have bigger and more grave issues to take note of and that punishing a comedian for a bad joke is uncalled for. </p><p>In a non-judgmental, very-objective way, Tanmay Bhat's little Snapchat stint wasn't exactly a humour fest--but the reaction that followed was nightmarish, to say the least. </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" style="background: rgb(255, 255, 255); margin: 1px; padding: 0px; border-radius: 3px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; width: calc(100% - 2px); max-width: 658px; box-shadow: 0px 0px 1px 0px rgba(0,0,0,0.5), 0px 1px 10px 0px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);" data-instgrm-captioned="" data-instgrm-version="7"><div style="padding: 8px;"> <div style="background: rgb(248, 248, 248); padding: 50% 0px; width: 100%; text-align: center; line-height: 0; margin-top: 40px;"> <div class="mceVisualAid" style='background: url("data:image/png;base64,"); margin: 0px auto -44px; top: -22px; width: 44px; height: 44px; display: block; position: relative;'></div></div> <p style="margin: 8px 0px 0px; padding: 0px 4px;"> <a style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); line-height: 17px; font-family: Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; text-decoration: none; -ms-word-wrap: break-word;" href="https://www.instagram.com/p/BGHx3_7ICIx/" target="_blank">My parents suggested not to put up this video .. But I don't want to live in fear .. And yes am Lata Ji hugest fan ??????</a></p> <p style="padding: 8px 0px 7px; text-align: center; color: rgb(201, 200, 205); line-height: 17px; overflow: hidden; font-family: Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 14px; margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: nowrap; -ms-text-overflow: ellipsis;">A video posted by Gaurav Gera (@gauravgera) on <time style="line-height: 17px; font-family: Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 14px;" datetime="2016-06-01T18:15:06+00:00">Jun 1, 2016 at 11:15am PDT</time></p></div></blockquote>
<script src="//platform.instagram.com/en_US/embeds.js" defer="" async=""></script><p><b>Also Read: <a href="http://indiatoday.intoday.in/story/asha-bhosle-grandson-on-tanmay-bhat-video/1/682613.html" target="_blank" mce_href="http://indiatoday.intoday.in/story/asha-bhosle-grandson-on-tanmay-bhat-video/1/682613.html"><u>Asha Bhosle's grandson on Tanmay Bhat video: It wasn't funny, but we don't want an apology</u></a> </b></p><p>The controversy that was considered important enough to dominate primetime news and have a full-fledged Facebook trend dedicated to itself caught speed when AIB comedian Tanmay Bhat posted a video on his Snapchat and Facebook accounts featuring some rather unfunny jokes on Sachin Tendulkar and Lata Mangeshkar. </p><p>The jokes didn't go down too well with a few Bollywood actors like Anupam Kher, Riteish Deshmukh and Celina Jaitley, who labelled the act 'disrespectful', 'offensive' and 'downright insulting'.<br /></p>]]></storybody>
